doc_summary_long: SpaceX is taking a risk - and possibly gaining a huge reward - by developing a satellite internet constellation. With several companies aiming to launch similar satellite constellations, SpaceX could take a slice of the market. If extra capacity is available during a customer launch, SpaceX could even launch its own small satellites on those missions.
doc_summary_short: SpaceX is taking a risk - and possibly gaining a huge reward - by developing a satellite internet constellation.
doc_title: SpaceX bets the house to become satellite internet provider
